OL,3,CVapes four times more profitable than
OL,4,Ctobacco to convenience stores ` study
OL,6,FVapes are four times more profitable
OL,7,Fto convenience stores than tobacco
OL,8,Famid a nine-fold increase in sales of
OL,9,Fthe devices in three years, according
OL,10,Fto a study.
OL,12,FConvenience stores make an average
OL,13,Fprofit of 37.1% for vape products
OL,14,Fcompared with 8.5% for tobacco
OL,15,Fproducts, figures from September 2022
OL,16,Fanalysed by the University of
OL,17,FEdinburgh show.
