OL,3,CVapes four times more profitable than
OL,4,Ctobacco to convenience stores ` study
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the average weekly number
OL,7,Fof transactions per store which
OL,8,Fincluded vapes rose sharply from 10 in
OL,9,F2019 to 93 in 2022 ` a nine-fold
OL,10,Fincrease in three years.
OL,12,FThe researchers noted it was likely
OL,13,Fthat sales from vapes had continued to
OL,14,Fgrow for small retailers since 2022.
OL,16,FFootfall from tobacco sales has
OL,17,Fdecreased by nearly 40% in small
OL,18,Fretail outlets compared to less than a
OL,19,Fdecade ago, the study shows.
