OL,6,FSome 21% of transactions included
OL,7,Ftobacco in 2015 when Action on Smoking
OL,8,Fand Health (Ash) conducted a similar
OL,9,Fanalysis, but this dropped to 12.8% in
OL,10,F2022, the University of Edinburgh
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FSome 16% of UK adults smoked in 2016,
OL,14,Fcompared to 12% in 2023, according to
OL,15,FOffice for National Statistics figures.
