OL,3,CVapes four times more profitable than
OL,4,Ctobacco to convenience stores ` study
OL,6,FThe study highlighted the potential
OL,7,Fbenefits to small retailers of
OL,8,Fexisting smokers switching to vaping,
OL,9,Fand showed that tobacco sales were
OL,10,Fbecoming increasingly unimportant for
OL,11,Fbusinesses, the authors said.
OL,13,FThe profitability of vapes also
OL,14,Funderscored the need for a retail
OL,15,Flicensing scheme to crack down on
OL,16,Firresponsible sellers and protect
OL,17,Flegitimate retailers.
