OL,3,CVapes four times more profitable than
OL,4,Ctobacco to convenience stores ` study
OL,6,FProfessor Jamie Pearce, professor of
OL,7,Fhealth geography at the University of
OL,8,FEdinburgh, said: "Our analysis shows
OL,9,Fthat convenience stores now make only
OL,10,F10% of their profits from tobacco and
OL,11,Fif their customers were buying
OL,12,Fproducts other than tobacco stores
OL,13,Fwould benefit from this.
OL,15,F"Sometimes business and public health
OL,16,Finterests align ` we would all be
OL,17,Fbetter off if fewer people bought
OL,18,Ftobacco."
