OL,3,CVapes four times more profitable than
OL,4,Ctobacco to convenience stores ` study
OL,6,FAsh chief executive Hazel Cheeseman
OL,7,Fsaid: "Tobacco is yesterday's product.
OL,8,FThe reduction in sales benefits both
OL,9,Fthe nation's health and convenience
OL,10,Fstores who make dwindling profits from
OL,11,Fselling tobacco. At the same time vape
OL,12,Fsales have surged, and this is much
OL,13,Fmore profitable for retailers.
OL,15,F"Responsible retailers who are already
OL,16,Fprofiting from vapes should welcome
OL,17,Fregulations to improve the market,
OL,18,Freduce appeal to children and drive
OL,19,Fout rogue traders."
