OL,6,FThe Tobacco and Vapes Bill is making
OL,7,Fits way through Parliament, which
OL,8,Fwould prevent anyone born after
OL,9,FJanuary 1 2009 from legally smoking by
OL,10,Fgradually raising the age at which
OL,11,Ftobacco can be bought.
OL,13,FIt also restricts sweet vape flavours
OL,14,Fand will review the packaging of e-
OL,15,Fcigarettes to reduce their appeal to
OL,16,Fchildren and young people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
